data.description: BEAUTIFUL, 4 Bedroom 2 1/2 Bath. Spacious Gameroom upstairs. Great for a Media Room. New flooring throughout the home. New Double oven and Microwave. Foam Insulation throughout the home, Attic has been decked for extra storage. Sprinkler System. Large Covered PATIO, FOR ALL YOUR FAMILY GET TOGETHER'S.  Back Yard is big enough for a pool. The home is located in the Highly Acclaimed Tomball School District. Schools are in the neighborhood. Easy Access to 249 and the Grand Parkway.
